{"tid":1390104,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"PC 9203嘅行為只係一場公關表演，各位校友唔好用嚟打飛機","createTime":"2019-07-31T05:17:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T10:54:54.000Z","uid":105779,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fdcf799df747808192fc97229501ef7dfd363035","tid":1390104,"uid":105779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:17:13.000Z","msg":"琴日小弟在場，班仆街放飛彈果時，PC 9203喱位｢傑出校友」同佢班同事一直留喺閘內。市民們嘅恐慌﹑受傷，佢哋完全視若無睹。指揮路面交通﹑檢查可疑車輛﹑照顧傷者﹑維持現場秩序等工作，由現場市民指揮咗好耐。<br />\n<br />\n直至消防﹑救護出車，佢哋先慢條斯理咁派幾個人出嚟。坦白講，果時大家嘅情緒已經平復咗好多，要驚一早驚完，阿｢傑出校友｣叫啲人唔駛驚﹑指揮交通等等只係出嚟交戲(隔離就係消防局，唔做下樣今日又畀人寫) 。<br />\n<br />\n香港警察冇個好人，到而家喱一刻都係，大家唔好畀佢哋嘅公關show混淆視聽。<br />\n請繼續恥與警察為伍。"},{"pid":"fd2d442b871041ebd99875ede848ae4c429047fd","tid":1390104,"uid":173326,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:18:59.000Z","msg":"俾大家清醒下<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8bZrWqF.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8bZrWqF.gif&h=e9acd895&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QZQrxuh.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQZQrxuh.gif&h=e8894b85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oq12Qho.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOq12Qho.gif&h=0b0f27fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8UOTWV1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8UOTWV1.gif&h=29319b79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XQQWagB.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXQQWagB.gif&h=67e696b8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c383bbf2537b7a74c237c599e1394a5ff18fb18b","tid":1390104,"uid":105779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:27:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54f2ebe8ffd9db438c66daf5dbdfdfb429883854","tid":1390104,"uid":276191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci